\Rightarrow\qquad 4 - 12t + 9t^2 + 9 - 36t + 36t^2 + 16 - 56t + 49t^2 & = 1 \\
\Rightarrow\qquad 94t^2 - 104t + 28 & = 0 \\
\Rightarrow\qquad 47t^2 - 52t + 14 & = 0
